.TH LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-BOTH-RESERVES-VARIANCE 1
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-both-reserves-variance \- variance of both reserve amounts across channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
lightning channel-both-reserves-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the variance of combined local and remote reserve amounts in millisatoshis.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with key both_reserves_variance_msat.
